  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Based on fundamental study （in Vitro and in Vivo, Pro. Jianjian Li）， Her2 expression would be
      changed from negative to positive by cancer irradiation with liner-accelerator at dose 6GY or
      up. The propose of this study is to reveal the irradiation result on Her2 expression in human
      breast cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Suspended</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    No Her-2 changes was found in Her-2 negative human breast cancer after radiotherapy
  </why_stopped>
